{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-tailwind-pricing-component/step-11","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-tailwind-pricing-component","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 11","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Iz standardnog CSS, naučili ste da postavljanje vrednosti display za element pomoću <code>grid</code> ništa ne radi sve dok ne postavite redove i kolone mreže. To takođe funkcioniše u Tailwind-u.</p>\n<p>U Tailwind-u, za postavljanje redova i kolona mreže (grid), koristićeš njihove klase utiliteta kao što sledi:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;div class=\"grid grid-cols-[num] grid-rows-[num]\">\n  &#x3C;div>Grid Item&#x3C;/div>\n  &#x3C;div>Grid Item&#x3C;/div>\n  &#x3C;div>Grid Item&#x3C;/div>\n&#x3C;/div>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Postavite klase servisa <code>div</code> i <code>grid-cols-1</code> za paket <code>md:grid-cols-3</code>.</p>\n<p>Darasa la <code>grid-cols-1</code> postavlja tri elementa u jednom redu, složeno vertikalno. Na srednjim i većim ekranima, <code>md:grid-cols-3</code> menja raspored u tri kolone, prikazujući elemente jedan pored drugog.</p>\n</section>","id":"6864df7ec0fc508ac3828ab5","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-tailwind-pricing-component/step-11"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Music App Pricing</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n  </